title: Independent Candidate Osama Gujjar wins PP-282 election
content:
ISLAMABAD, Feb 10 (APP): Independent Candidate, Osama Asghar Ali Gujjar has won the Punjab Assembly election from PP-282, Layyah-IV by securing 53,887 votes.
According to the unofficial result issued by the Returning Officer/ECP, his runner-up was Hashim Hussain, an independent candidate who bagged 27,384 votes.
Overall votersâ€™ turn-out remained 59.02%.
